Voicesphere,is,a,voice,control,platform,Voicesphere,can,be,used,as,an,application,on,mobile,devices,or,as,a,platform,for,developers,to,integrate,into,applications,The,Voicesphere,API,allows,developers,to,access,and,integrate,the,functionality,of,Voicesphere,with,other,applications,and,to,create,voice,controlled,applications,Some,example,API,methods,include,retrieving,calls,sending,requests,and,managing,responses